{"tid":1768603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲戰線 Magnitsky Act 開始立法咨詢","createTime":"2019-12-04T07:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T08:19:24.000Z","uid":165683,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b84738355878aedf464c50b54e87db7d2190c6f1","tid":1768603,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"大專學界代表團今日剛剛收到澳洲議會通知，澳洲外相Marise Payne已下令澳洲議會底下的外交丶國防及貿易委員會(Joint Standing Committee on Foreign Affairs, Defense and Trade) 進行有關Magnitsky Act的立法咨詢。<br />\n咨詢期至明年2020年1月31日，各位可以提交意見書並電郵至 jscfadt@aph.gov.au 。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足快啲做嘢！<br />\n<br />\n大專學界過去兩個月已經先後兩次到坎培拉進行游說工作，亦是第一批在六月反送中運動爆發後到訪澳洲推動Magnitsky Act的港人團體。<br />\n我們會繼續為大家繼續留意澳洲最新消息，一定要令全球圍堵中國。"},{"pid":"3803e5e98139dc7a54da7e24fe88f60c84b9fe7c","tid":1768603,"uid":321709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"692de5ac612137770f755de2c12fe9c86c969b5f","tid":1768603,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"已sent"},{"pid":"bd386ec2d45255c93683d56ab6211a9f44615d1d","tid":1768603,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3803e5e98139dc7a54da7e24fe88f60c84b9fe7c","tid":1768603,"uid":321709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"Agree <br />\n好可能work"},{"pid":"6de7498e8bfe5eb50c074475e8d02bfe11e1c93d","tid":1768603,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3803e5e98139dc7a54da7e2